&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recent experience managing and closing complex software sales within Public Sector customers in any of the Nordic markets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
